values.value:
01-25-23 Per discussion with Keith. We won't run after this; If he accepts CF Q it

His brother’s property; died in October  No Will;  In Probate; signed documents asking it to be released for sale.  Had to do a deep search.  I have Propstream eval which is $34000 and Zillow Assessed $77504.  He claims it is in excellent condition. Asked for Mfg. age, Tongue is on.  No mortgage or liens.  Thinking they are close to having it released to him..  Could be worth half the assessment.  Assessments are sometimes extremely high.

config.description:
This field is automated but can be updated manually.

- UNTOUCHED
Call them today!
*To prevent them from being marked as untouched in the future, initiate a followup sequence or set a followup date for a future date.

- RESPOND TO SELLER
This lead has either called/texted/emailed in and is waiting for your response.

- COMMITMENT COMPLETED
Your commitment to this lead today is complete. They will be marked as untouched the following day unless they are on a sequence or a followup date is set for a future date.

*Your Hierarchy will display all leads that are in Untouched or Respond to Seller.
